# speckit.plan - Evolution of Todo Architecture

## Phase II: Monorepo Architecture
```
hackathon-todo/
├── backend/            # FastAPI + SQLModel
│   ├── main.py        # Entry point
│   ├── models.py      # SQLModel definitions
│   └── auth.py        # JWT Verification middleware
├── frontend/           # Next.js + Better Auth
│   ├── app/           # App Router
│   └── components/    # Reusable UI
```

## Database Schema (SQLModel)
- **User**: Managed by Better Auth.
- **Task**: 
    - id: int (PK)
    - user_id: str (Indexed)
    - title: str (1-200)
    - description: str (0-1000)
    - completed: bool
    - created_at: datetime
    - updated_at: datetime

## AI Agent Integration (Phase III)
- **Agents**: CoreOrchestrator (OpenAI SDK).
- **Tools**: MCP Server exposing `add_task`, `list_tasks`, etc.

## Infrastructure (Phase IV/V)
- **Dapr Sidecar**: Pub/Sub (Kafka), Secrets (K8s), State (Redis/PG).
- **Kafka Topics**: `task-events`, `reminders`.
